# NETWORK::NETWORK_DOES_NETWORK_ID_EXIST

## Summary
Returns true if an entity (ped/vehicle/object) with the specified network ID exists on the local machine

## Parameters
* **NETWORK_INDEX** networkId

## Returns
* **BOOL**
